  • It's hoodie season!

    This Japanese Anime hoodie is sure to give your look a chilled kawaii edge. Featuring Jiji the black cat sitting on Kiki's magical broomstick on the front of the hoodie. Mix and match with any outfit!

    Choose between 12 different colors. We always recommend choosing 1 size up giving you the oversized hoodie look.

    Get ready to give your look a kawaii-style with this hoodie!

    Everyone will fall in love with this Kiki's Delivery Service unisex hoodie! It features a unique, high-quality design that is both stylish and cute. Made from premium polyester, it feels soft and smooth on the skin for all-day comfort, and the kawaii design will certainly get you noticed. Perfect for wearing around the house or while you're out and about.
